    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地下城、黑暗与压力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>打开大门，踏入一片新区域。<br>除此之外，未知的危险和探索的回报也在等待着你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/392937f6212dcff96c456aea9228eb48.poster.avif?t=1769831703\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/392937f6212dcff96c456aea9228eb48.webm?t=1769831703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/392937f6212dcff96c456aea9228eb48.mp4?t=1769831703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>潜伏在地下城各处的威胁绝对会让你毫不放松警惕。<br>在充满压力的游戏中，通过真实的魂系列战斗击败你的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/4af8a4a571b38ab02ccb5a704a440044.poster.avif?t=1769831703\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/4af8a4a571b38ab02ccb5a704a440044.webm?t=1769831703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/4af8a4a571b38ab02ccb5a704a440044.mp4?t=1769831703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>地下城如同蜘蛛网般紧密相连。<br>你将在不断的死亡中坠入迷宫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/dce729cd56b1cd4f9a60db0dbb61e1a1.poster.avif?t=1769831703\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045730/extras/dce729cd56b1cd4f9a60db0dbb61e1